description: Retrieves the results for a given media analysis job. Takes a JobId returned by StartMediaAnalysisJob.

parameters.name: JobId
parameters.description: Unique identifier for the media analysis job for which you want to retrieve results.

nested_items.name: JobId
nested_items.description: The identifier for the media analysis job.

nested_items.name: JobName
nested_items.description: The name of the media analysis job.

nested_items.name: OperationsConfig
nested_items.description: Operation configurations that were provided during job creation.

nested_items.name: DetectModerationLabels
nested_items.description: Contains configuration options for a DetectModerationLabels job.

nested_items.name: MinConfidence
nested_items.description: Specifies the minimum confidence level for the moderation labels to return. Amazon Rekognition doesn't return any labels with a confidence level lower than this specified value.

nested_items.name: ProjectVersion
nested_items.description: Specifies the custom moderation model to be used during the label detection job. If not provided the pre-trained model is used.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The current status of the media analysis job.

nested_items.name: FailureDetails
nested_items.description: Details about the error that resulted in failure of the job.

nested_items.name: Code
nested_items.description: Error code for the failed job.

nested_items.name: Message
nested_items.description: Human readable error message.

nested_items.name: CreationTimestamp
nested_items.description: The Unix date and time when the job was started.

nested_items.name: CompletionTimestamp
nested_items.description: The Unix date and time when the job finished.

nested_items.name: Bucket
nested_items.description: Name of the S3 bucket.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: S3 object key name.

nested_items.name: Version
nested_items.description: If the bucket is versioning enabled, you can specify the object version.

nested_items.name: OutputConfig
nested_items.description: Output configuration that was provided in the creation request.

nested_items.name: S3Bucket
nested_items.description: Specifies the Amazon S3 bucket to contain the output of the media analysis job.

nested_items.name: S3KeyPrefix
nested_items.description: Specifies the Amazon S3 key prefix that comes after the name of the bucket you have designated for storage.

nested_items.name: KmsKeyId
nested_items.description: KMS Key that was provided in the creation request.

nested_items.name: Bucket
nested_items.description: Name of the S3 bucket.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: S3 object key name.

nested_items.name: Version
nested_items.description: If the bucket is versioning enabled, you can specify the object version.

nested_items.name: ModelVersions
nested_items.description: Information about the model versions for the features selected in a given job.

nested_items.name: Moderation
nested_items.description: The Moderation base model version.

nested_items.name: ManifestSummary
nested_items.description: The summary manifest provides statistics on input manifest and errors identified in the input manifest.

nested_items.description: Name of the S3 bucket.
